All Implemented Interfaces:
Placeable
public class EnchantmentRune extends SimpleSlimefunItem<ItemDropHandler>
This SlimefunItem allows you to enchant any enchantable ItemStack with a random Enchantment. It is also one of the very few utilisations of ItemDropHandler.
